Sqemes self-host bundle
=======================

This directory bundles Sqemes (Apache-2.0) with configuration vendored from the
Supabase self-hosting Docker setup.

Vendored from supabase/supabase (https://github.com/supabase/supabase), directory
`docker/`, licensed under the Apache License 2.0:

  - docker-compose.yml
  - volumes/api/kong.yml, volumes/api/kong-entrypoint.sh
  - volumes/db/*.sql
  - volumes/pooler/pooler.exs
  - volumes/functions/main/index.ts   (also copied to edge-main/index.ts)
  - utils/generate-keys.sh

Retrieved from branch `master` on 2026-07-12. These files carry their original
Apache-2.0 license; see https://github.com/supabase/supabase/blob/master/LICENSE.

Sqemes-authored files in this directory (docker-compose.sqemes.yml, Dockerfile.app,
nginx.conf, init/apply.sh, .env.example additions, README.md) are part of Sqemes and
licensed under Apache-2.0 (see ../LICENSE).
